śītārtas+yavamālī ca &rāvaṇas+rākṣasākṛtis+|
yajvādātā tathā hotā &bhoktā bhogapatis+tathā|| 955 ||

ete prādhānyatas+rājan+ &nāgeśās+kīrtitās+mayā|
eteṣām+yat+parīvāram+ &putrapautrādikam+ca yat|| 956 ||

na tat+śakyam+mayā rājan+ &vaktum+varṣaśatais+api|
sarveṣām+eva nāgānām+ &puṇyāni bhavanāni+uta|| 957 ||

sarve varapradās+nāgās+ &sarve nīlam+anuvratās+|
sarve+atidayitās+rājan+ &vāsukes+sumahātmanas+|| 958 ||

dikpālān+atha te vakṣye &kaśmīrāyām+nibodha tān|
pūrvasyām+diśi rājendra &nāgas+bindusaras+smṛtas+|| 959 ||

dakṣiṇena tathā nāgas+ &nāmnā śrīmāḍhakas+smṛtas+|
uttareṇa tathā rājan+ &proktas+tu+uttaramānasas+|| 960 ||

paścimena ca rājendra &nāmnā+ailāpatras+ucyate|
evam+nāgasahasrāṇi &prayutāni+arbudāni ca|| 961 ||

tārkṣyajam+tu bhayam+tyaktvā &vasanti+iha gatavyathās+|
ye ca+uktās+tu mayā nāgās+ &teṣām+madhyāt+ṣaḍaṅgulas+|| 962 ||

ekas+vivāsitas+rājñā &nīlena+amitatejasā|
sthānam+ṣāḍaṅgulam+rājan+ &mahāpadmasya dhīmatas+|| 963 ||

tṛtīyasya tu yat+dattam+ &tatra jātam+jalāśayam|
yojanāyāmavistāram+ &samudram+iva ca+aparam|| 964 ||

chadmanā+apahṛtam+yat+ca &mahāpadmena pārthiva|
nīlasya+anumate pūrvam+ &viṣvagaśvāt+narādhipāt|| 965 ||

iti nīlamate nāgāyatanakīrtanam|

gonandas+uvāca |

ṣaḍaṅgulas+katham+rājñā &nīlena+asmāt+vivāsitas+|
katham+ca viṣvagaśvasya &sthānam+jātam+jalāśayam|
etat+sarvam+samācakṣva &kuśalas+hi+asi dhārmika|| 966 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

pūrvam+eva satīdeśe &mahāpadmam+bhujaṃgamam|
viditvā+eva kṛtasthānam+ &vainateyas+hi+abādhata|| 967 ||

tasya putrān+tathā sarvān+ &āśritopāśritān+khagas+|
ākramya bhakṣayāmāsa &śataśas+atha sahasraśas+|| 968 ||

svajane bhakṣyamāne+atha &mahāpadmas+bhujaṃgamas+|
ājagāma mahānāgam+ &nīlam+śaraṇam+añjasā|| 969 ||

sthānam+ca prārthayāmāsa &kaśmīrāyām+janeśvara|
tam+uvāca tadā nīlas+ &mahāpadmam+bhujaṃgamam|| 970 ||

nāgās+bhujaṃgaśārdūla &sarve teha kṛtālayās+|
na+asti sthānam+tu vasasi &yatra nāgendrasattama|| 971 ||

na tam+deśam+prapaśyāmi &sūkṣmam+api+amaraprabha|
nāgais+na+adhiṣṭhitam+yat+tu &sarvam+eva bhujaṃgama|| 972 ||

parīvāreṇa bahunā &tathā tvam+parivāritas+|
kim+tu+asti sāmpratam+śūnyam+ &sthānam+ṣāḍaṅgulam+śubham|| 973 ||

mayā nirvāsitas+nāgas+ &tasmāt+deśāt+ṣaḍaṅgulas+|
mānuṣāṇām+sa dārāṇi &harati+aharahas+purā|| 974 ||

itas+nirvāsya dattam+ca &sthānam+tasya tatas+mayā|
uśīrake giriśreṣṭhe &dārveṣu bhujagottama|| 975 ||

mayā+api sthānapālas+asau &yuktyā tatra niveśitas+|
gṛhītas+ca+anurāgeṇa &janas+kāśmīrakas+mayā|| 976 ||

ṣaḍaṅgulas+ca nāgendras+ &same pathi niveśitas+|
pūjyamānas+janais+tatra &sukham+āste ṣaḍaṅgulas+|| 977 ||

madvākyāt+ca+abhayam+dattam+ &tatra+asya hariṇā svayam|
sthāne ṣāḍaṅgule ramye &viṣvagaśvasya bhūpates+|| 978 ||

yat+etat+nagaram+ramyam+ &nāmnā candrapuram+puram|
atra te dadmi vasatim+ &kuru tatra jalāśayam|| 979 ||

sthāne ṣāḍaṅgule ramye &durvāsās+munisattamas+|
unmattaveṣas+pracchannas+ &na+āptavān+sampratiśrayam|| 980 ||

śaptam+tena saroṣeṇa &bhavitā+idam+jalāśayam|
na ca+api viditam+nāga &munivākyam+tu kasyacit|| 981 ||

mayā+eva kevalam+jñātam+ &tasya+eva+anugrahāt+munes+|
tasmāt+tvam+vasatim+tatra &kuru pannaga mā+aciram|| 982 ||

kim+tu+abhyarthaya bhūpālam+ &viṣvagaśvam+narādhipam|
chadmanā yācanam+tasya &tvayā kāryam+mahīpates+|| 983 ||

sa+chadmanā yācyamānas+ &lobhāt+yas+na pradāsyati|
avaśyakaraṇīye+arthe &pārthivas+syāt+vimānitas+|| 984 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

evam+uktas+tu nīlena &mahāpadmas+bhujaṃgamas+|
bhūtvā tu brāhmaṇas+vṛddhas+ &yayau candrapuram+puram|| 985 ||

sa dadarśa mahīnātham+ &viṣvagaśvam+dayāparam|
dṛṣṭvā ca+ayācata tadā &yathā viṣṇus+balim+tathā|| 986 ||

brāhmaṇas+uvāca |

rājan+candrapure śubhas+ &dīyatām+me pratiśrayas+|
paryāptam+yat+kuṭumbasya &mahatas+me dayāpara|| 987 ||

viṣvagaśvas+uvāca |

dadāni te+aham+viprendra &sthānam+candrapure+śubham|
gṛhāṇa yāvat+paryāptam+ &sakuṭumbasya te dvija|| 988 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

pratigrahajalam+gṛhya &svastivācya bhujaṃgamas+|
uvāca mantriṇām+madhye &nāgarūpe narādhipam|| 989 ||

hastyaśvarathasaṃyuktas+ &svajanais+parivāritas+|
niryāhi nagarāt+asmāt+ &sadhanadravyasaṃcayas+|| 990 ||

sakuṭumbasya paryāptam+ &nagaram+me narādhipa|
jalāśayas+suvistīrṇas+ &bhavitā śīghram+eva tu|| 991 ||

tatas+sa rājā dharmātmā &sapaurahayakuñjaras+|
sārthamātracayas+gatvā &svapurāt+yojanadvayam|
paścimena tadā cakre &nagaram+sumanoharam|| 992 ||

viṣvagaśvapuram+nāma &tat+etat+bhuvi viśrutam|
tatra+uvāsa sukhī rājā &brāhmaṇān+paripūjayan|| 993 ||

nagaram+plāvayāmāsa &mahāpadmas+bhujaṃgamas+|
tatra+āste saparīvāras+ &sukhī bhujagasattamas+|| 994 ||

mahāpadmasaras+tat+ca &yojanāyāmavistṛtam|
supuṇyam+ramaṇīyam+ca &satām+hṛdayanandanam|| 995 ||

mahāpadmaprabhāvena &duṣṭagrahavivarjitam|
tatra+āste sa sukhī nāgas+ &kuṭumbaparivāritas+|| 996 ||

mahāpadmasarasya+eṣa &kathitas+sambhavas+mayā|
kim+anyat+tava rājendra &kathayāmi vadasva tat|| 997 ||

iti nīlamate mahāpadmapraveśas+|

gonandas+uvāca |

bhagavan+śrotum+icchāmi &puṇyāni+āyatanāni+aham|
kāśmīreṣu ca deśeṣu &darśanam+samprakīrtaya|| 998 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

vināyakam+tu gāṅgeyam+ &niḥsṛtam+vardhanadrumāt|
tam+dṛṣṭvā sarvakalyānīm+ &siddhim+āpnoti mānavas+|| 999 ||

tathāvidham+kāmyavaram+ &tasya dakṣiṇapaścime|
deśe tu krośamātreṇa &dṛṣṭvā kāryāṇi sādhayet|| 1000 ||

bhūrjasvāmi hiḍimbeśas+ &lovāras+śrīvināyakas+|
utaṅkeśas+guhāvāsī &bhīmeśas+saumukhas+tathā|| 1001 ||

bhadreśvaras+mahāsyas+ca &mahāśanagaveṣiṇau|
paulastyas+girivāsī ca &jayeśvaramaheśvarau|| 1002 ||

ekaikam+ebhyas+dṛṣṭvā tu &gaṇeśam+susamāhitas+|
kāryasiddhim+avāpnoti &puṇyam+phalam+upāśnute|| 1003 ||

śacyās+samīpe paulastyam+ &dṛṣṭvā skandam+narādhipa|
pātrakuṇḍe naras+snātvā &kaumāram+lokam+āpnuyāt|| 1004 ||

mālīvaram+gautameśam+ &viśvāmitreśvaram+tathā|
saunāsikam+vasiṣṭheśam+ &mākhareśam+sureśvaram|| 1005 ||

skandeśvaram+viśākheśam+ &paulastyam+aparam+tathā|
dṛṣṭvā kumāram+ekaikam+ &phalam+godānajam+labhet|| 1006 ||

pulastyanirmitam+śakram+ &bharadvājakṛtam+tathā|
kāśyapam+kāṇvam+āgastyam+ &vāsiṣṭham+ca śatakratum|| 1007 ||

dṛṣṭvā svargam+avāpnoti &gosahasraphalam+labhet|
agnes+āṅgirasīm+dṛṣṭvā &pratimām+prāpnuyāt+divam|| 1008 ||

aujase tu naras+snātvā &dṛṣṭvā pretādhipam+yamam|
svargalokam+avāpnoti &tiladhenuphalam+labhet|| 1009 ||

snātvā tu puṣkare tīrthe &dṛṣṭvā sūryasutam+tathā|
sarvapāpavinirmuktas+ &svargaloke mahīyate|| 1010 ||

pretādhipam+vāsiṣṭham+ca &utaṅkeśam+tathā yamam|
dṛṣṭvā+ekaikam+atha+etebhyas+ &mucyate sarvakilbiṣais+|| 1011 ||

tārārātryām+viśeṣeṇa &dṛṣṭvā hi+ete mahābalās+|
dṛṣṭvā tam+arcitam+devam+ &virūpākṣam+iti śrutam|| 1012 ||

na+āpnoti sarvakāleṣu &bhayam+rākṣasasambhavam|
dṛṣṭvā tu varuṇam+devam+ &rājan+ca balinā kṛtam|| 1013 ||

sarvapāpavinirmuktas+ &vāruṇam+lokam+aśnute|
mānasasya+uttare kūle &mahāpadmajalāśaye|| 1014 ||

snātvā dṛṣṭvā+eva bhavanam+ &pulastyena vinirmitam|
godānaphalam+āpnoti &vyādhibhis+ca vimucyate|| 1015 ||

dṛṣṭvā dhaneśvaram+devam+ &vitastākhyasamīpatas+|
kapaṭeśvarapārśve ca &dṛṣṭvā+agastyena nirmitam|| 1016 ||

setāram+gotamasvāmim+ &saumukham+surabhīkṛtam|
dṛṣṭvā+ekaikam+atha+etebhyas+ &dhanavān+abhijāyate|| 1017 ||

dṛṣṭvā śaśāṅkam+rājñā tu &sucandreṇa vinirmitam|
candralokam+avāpnoti &naras+na+asti+atra saṃśayas+|| 1018 ||

maṇibhadram+tathā dṛṣṭvā &dhanavān+abhijāyate|
kāmadevam+agastyena &parvatopari nirmitam|| 1019 ||

dṛṣṭvā sukham+avāpnoti &rūpavān+abhijāyate|
pulastyanirmitā devī &bhuvi bheḍā+iti viśrutā|| 1020 ||

dṛṣṭvā tām+munivandyām+ca &phalam+prāpya manīṣitam|
sarvapāpavinirmuktas+ &vidyām+āpnoti anuttamām|| 1021 ||

dṛṣṭvā viśokām+kāśmīryām+ &keśavena+upabṛṃhitām|
pratiṣṭhitām+keśavena &viṣṇuloke mahīyate|| 1022 ||

bhīmadevīm+tathā dṛṣṭvā &śriyam+āpnoti+anuttamām|
tathā kapiñjalīm+devīm+ &tathā devīm+sureśvarīm|| 1023 ||

bhadreśvarīm+gautameśīm+ &devīm+kālaśilām+api|
tathā+udyogaśriyam+nāmnīm+ &gavākṣīm+caṇḍikām+api|| 1024 ||

durgām+gaurīm+suvijayām+ &śakunīm+brahmacāriṇīm|
cakreśvarīm+tathā dṛṣṭvā &manoratham+avāpnuyāt|| 1025 ||

cakrasvāmisamīpe ca &dṛṣṭvā devīm+harāṅkagām|
sarvapāpavinirmuktas+ &rudraloke mahīyate|| 1026 ||

kārtavīryārjunasvāmim+ &dṛṣṭvā tam+ca divākaram|
mārtāṇḍam+kaśyapasvāmim+ &viṣvagaśvakṛtam+ravim|| 1027 ||

sucandreśam+sucakreśam+ &surabhīsvāminam+ravim|
dṛṣṭvā+ekaikam+atha+etebhyas+ &hayadānaphalam+labhet|| 1028 ||

brahmāṇam+varadam+dṛṣṭvā &śailarūpadharam+svayam|
viṣṇusvāmim+harisvāmim+ &kaśyapasvāminam+tathā|| 1029 ||

dṛṣṭvā+etān+svargam+āpnoti &bhūmipāla pitāmahān|
cakrasvāmisamīpastham+ &harim+dṛṣṭvā sudarśanam|| 1030 ||

svayambhuvam+vahnikṛtam+ &tathā vai piṅgaleśvaram|
bindunādeśvaram+devam+ &devam+bhadreśvaram+tathā|| 1031 ||

candreśvaram+sajyeṣṭheśam+ &vālakhilyeśvaram+haram|
keśaveśam+sameśam+ca &dhaumyeśam+varuṇeśvaram|| 1032 ||

cakreśvaram+sacandreśam+ &kaśyapeśam+vilohitam|
kāmeśam+savasiṣṭheśam+ &bhūteśam+sagaṇeśvaram|| 1033 ||

sūryeśvaram+mahārāja &bhasmeśam+vimaleśvaram|
dṛṣṭvā+ekaikam+atha+etebhyas+ &mucyate sarvakilbiṣais+|| 1034 ||

himācaleśam+śaṅkheśam+ &devam+vaivaṭṭileśvaram|
mahānadīśvaram+śambhum+ &varadam+kaśyapeśvaram|| 1035 ||

rājeśvaram+nṛsiṃheśam+ &bhaveśam+dhanadeśvaram|
dṛṣṭvā+ekaikam+atha+etebhyas+ &mucyate sarvakilbiṣais+|| 1036 ||

sadā saṃnihitas+rājan+ &devas+bhūteśvaras+haras+|
mucyate kilbiṣais+sarvais+ &tatra dṛṣṭvā+eva nandinam|| 1037 ||

nandīśvare prasanne hi &sadā bhūteśvaras+tathā|
sāṃnidhyam+rājaśārdūla &[lacuna]|| 1038 ||

[lacuna] &lokānām+hitakāmyayā|
sadā saṃnihitas+tatra &nandī bhaktyā harasya tu|| 1039 ||

toyamadhyagatam+dṛṣṭvā &samprāpya kapaṭeśvaram|
gosahasram+avāpnoti &sampūjya+abhīpsitām+gatim|| 1040 ||

iti nīlamate devāyatanakīrtanam|

gonandas+uvāca |

katham+ārādhitas+devas+ &nandinā vadatām+vara|
nityam+saṃnihitas+devas+ &yena bhūteśvare sthitas+|| 1041 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

śṛṇu rājan+kathām+divyām+ &sarvakalmaṣanāśinīm|
nandinam+prati bhūpāla &yathāvṛttām+manoramām|| 1042 ||

śilādas+nāma vipras+abhūt+ &purā putravivarjitas+|
tena varṣaśatam+bhuktvā &śilācūrṇam+narādhipa|
nandiparvatam+āsādya &mahādevas+prasāditas+|| 1043 ||

putrārtham+tu tadā tasya &devadevas+anukampayā|
putratve nandinam+prādāt+ &svagaṇeśam+mahābalam|| 1044 ||

dīyamānas+tu putratve &nandī provāca śaṃkaram|
anugrahāt+dvijasya+asya &putras+aham+bhavitā prabho|| 1045 ||

kim+tu+ayonibhavas+deva &bhaveyam+tu+asya putrakas+|
ciram+ca na ca vatsye+aham+ &mānuṣye tvadvinākṛtas+|| 1046 ||

tam+uvāca haras+devas+ &prahasan+anukampayā|
umāvivāhe śaptas+asi &bhṛguṇā tvam+gaṇottama|| 1047 ||

apūjitena māṇuṣyam+ &tena+api bhavitā dhruvam|
tena ca+eva śarīreṇa &matsamīpam+upeṣyasi|| 1048 ||

tataḥprabhṛti mānuṣye &vatsyase tvam+gaṇottama|
vatsyase matsamīpe ca &prākāmyena yathāsukham|| 1049 ||

vatsyase kim+ca mānuṣye &bhṛguśāpabalātkṛtas+|
tatra+api te+aham+vatsyāmi &prākāmyena gaṇeśvara|| 1050 ||

evam+bhūteśvare nandī &nityam+vasati pārthiva|
prākāmyena haras+devas+ &tathā tadanukampayā|| 1051 ||

gonandas+uvāca |

katham+jātas+śilādasya &nandī putratvam+āgatas+|
katham+ca svaśarīreṇa &gāṇapatyam+avāptavān|| 1052 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

ayonijas+śilādena &śilām+cūrṇayatā tadā|
samprāptas+tu śilāmadhyāt+ &putras+nandī śaśiprabhas+|| 1053 ||

tam+prāpya tanayam+vipras+ &śilādas+harṣam+āgatas+|
saṃskārāṇi tu sarvāṇi &putrasya kṛtavān+tadā|| 1054 ||

kriyamāṇeṣu putrasya &saṃskāreṣu tadā dvijas+|
alpāyuṣam+sa śuśrāva &brāhmaṇebhyas+tadā sutam|| 1055 ||

śrutvā+arodat+sa dharmātmā &śilādas+putravatsalas+|
tam+rudantam+tadā nandī &vārayāmāsa dharmavit|| 1056 ||

mā tvam+rodasva tāta+adya &tava+aham+priyakāmyayā|
ārādhya śaṃkaram+devam+ &dīrgham+āpsyāmi jīvitam|| 1057 ||

evam+uktvā sa pitaram+ &prāptānujñas+tatas+svayam|
haramukuṭam+iti khyātam+ &śṛṅgam+himavatas+śubham|| 1058 ||

jagāma sahasā nandī &tapase kṛtaniścayas+|
yat+asti loke vikhyātam+ &gaṅgāprabhavam+uttamam|| 1059 ||

tasya śṛṅgasya pūrvārdhe &saras+asti vimalodakam|
kālodakam+iti khyātam+ &sarvakilbiṣanāśanam|| 1060 ||

tasmin+nandī śilām+gṛhya &gurvīm+mūdhani+atandritas+|
ārādhayāmāsa haram+ &rudrajāpaparatas+jale|| 1061 ||

tasya varṣaśatam+rudram+ &japatas+salile gatam|
tatas+varṣaśate pūrṇe &devī devam+abhāṣata|| 1062 ||

putras+me bhagavan+nandī &kālode tapyate tapas+|
varadānena tam+deva &yojayasva+āśu mā+aciram|| 1063 ||

evam+uktas+tadā devyā &vārāṇasyām+narādhipa|
devyā saha tatas+devas+ &mārgeṇa kṣitigāminā|| 1064 ||

prapede vṛṣabhārūḍhas+ &na ca+adṛśyata kenacit|
sa prayāgam+atikramya &tathā+ayodhyām+mahāpurīm|| 1065 ||

puṇyam+ca naimiṣāraṇyam+ &gaṅgādvāram+atas+param|
sthāneśvaram+kurukṣetram+ &tathā viṣṇupadam+śubham|| 1066 ||

śatadrum+ca vipāśām+ca &puṇyatoyām+irāvatīm|
devikām+candrabhāgām+ca &tathā viṣṇupadam+saras+|| 1067 ||

viśokām+vijayeśam+ca &vitastāsindhusaṃgamam|
etān+sarvān+atikramya &prayayau bharatam+girim|| 1068 ||

tasya mūlam+atha+āsādya &devyā vacanam+abravīt|
iha+eva tiṣṭha tāvat+tvam+ &aham+yāsyāmi+atas+param|| 1069 ||

vṛṣeṇa sahitā devi &parvate+asmin+hi yas+pathā|
karoti+ārohaṇam+tasya &mahat+puṇyaphalam+smṛtam|| 1070 ||

pathā tvam+na samarthā+asi &sukumārā+asi devi yat|
āroḍhum+tena yāsye+aham+ &ekas+eva+adya satvaras+|| 1071 ||

tasmāt+deśāt+pravṛttas+tu &gantum+devavaras+pathā|
patheśvarākhyas+tatra+iṣṭas+ &devasya+āyatanas+abhavat|| 1072 ||

āruroha pathā śailam+ &yadā devas+maheśvaras+|
tadā vṛddhim+āgāt+śailas+ &mahatīm+bhūridakṣiṇas+|| 1073 ||

vardhamānam+tu tam+jñātvā &śrāntas+kruddhas+maheśvaras+|
rūpam+kṛtvā mahat+ghoram+ &padā mūrdhani+atāḍayat|| 1074 ||

tataḥprabhṛti tat+śailam+ &muṇḍapṛṣṭham+prakīrtitam|
muṇḍapṛṣṭham+śarīreṇa &spṛṣṭvā sarveṇa mānuṣas+|| 1075 ||

aśubham+kīrtayitvā ca &tasmāt+pāpāt+pramucyate|
devena tāḍitas+śailas+ &rūpam+mānuṣyam+āsthitas+|| 1076 ||

prāñjalis+devadeveśam+ &uvāca kṛpaṇas+hi+aham|
tatas+prasannas+deveśas+ &śailam+āha kṛpānvitas+|| 1077 ||

mama pādaprahāreṇa &nirgatam+yat+jalam+tava|
kṛpāṇītīrtham+iti+etat+ &bhuvi yāsyati pārvata|| 1078 ||

muṇḍapṛṣṭham+girim+kṛtvā &saumyam+rūpam+atha+āsthitas+|
apsarobhis+yutas+yatra &tīrtham+apsarasām+hi tat|| 1079 ||

tatas+brahmasaras+nāma &dṛṣṭvā tīrtham+manoramam|
haṃsarūpadharas+śailam+ &pāṭayāmāsa satvaras+|| 1080 ||

haṃsarūpeṇa yat+śaile &kṛtam+chidram+mahātmanā|
haṃsadvāram+iti proktam+ &sarvakilbiṣanāśanam|| 1081 ||

dṛṣṭvā tīrthau mahādevas+ &tathā vāṭikaṣaṇḍikau|
kapilatīrtham+āsādya &sa dadarśa pitāmaham|
devais+vṛtam+mahābhāgam+ &yajantam+ṛṣibhis+tadā|| 1082 ||

haṃsarūpadharam+dṛṣṭvā &brahmā devam+maheśvaram|
jānubhyām+avanim+gatvā &vavande parameśvaram|| 1083 ||

dṛṣṭvā tu praṇatam+devam+ &brahmāṇam+jagatas+prabhum|
praṇamya śakras+provāca &yat+tat+śṛṇu mahīpate|| 1084 ||

śakras+uvāca |

namas+te devadeveśa &jagatkāraṇakāraṇa|
trailokyanātha sarvajña &sarveśvara namas+astu te|| 1085 ||

tvattas+anyam+na+eva paśyāmi &jagati+asmin+hi kāraṇam|
tvayā sarvam+idam+vyāptam+ &trailokyam+scarācaram|| 1086 ||

sraṣṭā tvam+asya sarvasya &saṃhartā pālakas+tathā|
yadā+unmīlayase netre &trailokyasya+udbhavas+tadā|| 1087 ||

bhavati+iha jagannātha &yadā ca svapiṣe vibho|
tat+etat+akhilam+sarvam+ &trailokyam+sampraṇaśyati|| 1088 ||

bhūmis+dhṛtā dhārayati &tvayā+idam+sacarācaram|
tvayā dhṛtā dhārayanti &tathā+eva+āpas+akhilam+jagat|| 1089 ||

tvattejasā jagat+sarvam+ &vahnis+dhārayate prabho|
tvattejasā tathā vāyus+ &dhārayati+akhilam+jagat|| 1090 ||

śabdayonim+tathā+ākāśam+ &jagat+dhārayate prabho|
vīryeṇa te mahābhāga &tvam+ca proktas+tathā+aparas+|| 1091 ||

tvam+vahnis+tvam+tathā+eva+ātmā &sarvasya+asya prakīrtitas+|
avyaktas+puruṣas+ca+eva &rajas+sattvam+tathā tamas+|
indriyāṇi+indriyārthās+ca &bhūtatanmātrasaṃjñakas+|| 1092 ||

jñātā jñeyam+tathā kṣetram+ &kṣetrajñas+parameśvaras+|
dhyātā dhyeyam+tathā dhyānam+ &yajñāni vividhāni ca|| 1093 ||

sarvam+etat+tvam+eva+ekas+ &tvattas+kim+aparam+prabho|
yat+natas+asi mahābhāga &etat+me saṃśayas+mahān|| 1094 ||

iti nīlamate śakrakṛtaśivastotram|

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

evam+uktas+tu śakreṇa &brahmā vacanam+abravīt|
eṣā tanus+dvitīyā me &śārvī paramapāvanī|| 1095 ||

tapasā mahatā yuktā &yat+natas+asmi śatakrato|
tvam+ca sarvais+surais+sākam+ &namaskṛtvā prasādaya|| 1096 ||

evam+uktas+tatas+śakras+ &sarvais+suragaṇais+vṛtas+|
tuṣṭāva devadeveśam+ &tripurāntakaram+haram|
prasādāt+brahmaṇas+tasya &yathātathyena śaṃkaram|| 1097 ||

śakras+uvāca |

namas+te devadeveśa &māyāvṛta jagattraya|
yajamānas+mahī kham+ca &toyāgnīndvarkavāyavas+|| 1098 ||

tanavas+te vinirdiṣṭās+ &yābhis+vyāptam+jagattrayam|
brāhmīm+tanum+tathā+āsthāya &rājasīm+tvam+jagadguro|| 1099 ||

lokān+sṛjasi bhūtātman+ &tava kāryam+na vidyate|
pauruṣīm+tanum+āsthāya &sāttvikīm+tvam+maheśvara|| 1100 ||

pālayasi+akhilam+deva &trailokyam+sākṣivat+sthitas+|
kālākhyam+tāmasīm+kṛtvā &jagat+saṃharase tathā|| 1101 ||

vṛṣarūpadharas+dharmas+ &vāhanatvam+tava+āgatas+|
vāmārdham+dayitākāyam+ &brahmacārī sadā bhavān|| 1102 ||

namas+śaśāṅkalekhāṅka &jagadyone maheśvara|
gaṅgātaraṅganirdhūta- &jaṭābhāra namas+astu te|| 1103 ||

tripurāre namas+te+astu &namas+tu+andhakaghātine|
śūlāgrabhinnadaityāṃsa- &rudhirārdra namas+astu te|| 1104 ||

kapālamāline tubhyam+ &pārvatīdayitāya ca|
ugrāyudhāya bhīmāya &bhīmāyudhadharāya ca|| 1105 ||

ūrdhvaliṅgāya śīghrāya &krathāya krathanāya ca|
maṅgalyāya vareṇyāya &mahāhaṃsāya mīḍhuṣe|
bhīmākṣāya bhusuṇḍāya &vyālayajñopavītine|| 1106 ||

kṣamasva mama deveśa &yat+mayā+asi na pūjitas+|
tava+eva māyayā pūrvam+ &mohitena jagatprabho|| 1107 ||

prasannas+asi dhruvam+śambho &yena jñātas+asi vai mayā|
suprasādas+asi deveśa &praṇatas+asmi maheśvara|| 1108 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

evam+stutas+tu śakreṇa &brahmaṇā ṛṣibhis+surais+|
haṃsarūpam+tadā tyaktvā &svena rūpeṇa śaṃkaras+|| 1109 ||

jagāma brahmaṇas+yajñam+ &devānām+darśanam+dadau|
ānāyayāmāsa tadā &devīm+devas+vṛṣam+tathā|| 1110 ||

tatra+eva devadeveśas+ &samāpte brahmaṇas+kratau|
sarvais+devagaṇais+sārdham+ &yayau kālodakam+saras+|| 1111 ||

dadarśa nandinam+tatra &śītakṣudbhāvakarṣitam|
mṛtyunā+anvīyamānam+ca &bandhunā+iva narādhipa|| 1112 ||

dṛṣṭvā+uvāca mahādevas+ &nandinam+japatām+varam|
varam+varaya bhadram+te &uttiṣṭha+uttiṣṭha putraka|| 1113 ||

dṛṣṭvā devam+haram+devyā &pārvatyā saha saṃsthitam|
sarvais+devagaṇais+sārdham+ &tatyāja maraṇāt+bhayam|| 1114 ||

śilām+tyaktvā samutthāya &toyamadhyāt+sasambhramam|
pūjayāmāsa deveśam+ &vāgbhis+adbhis+tathā+eva ca|| 1115 ||

pūjitas+śaṃkaras+tena &prahasan+vākyam+abravīt|
rudrajapena te tāta &tapasā mahatā tathā|| 1116 ||

parituṣṭas+asmi bhadram+te &matsamīpe nivatsyasi|
anena+eva śarīreṇa &na+asti te mṛtyutas+bhayam|| 1117 ||

smarasva pūrvakam+janma &pratīhāras+bhavān+mama|
śilādena dvijendreṇa &prāptas+tvam+tapasā tadā|| 1118 ||

tatputreṇa tvayā putra &śilādas+tāritas+tathā|
gaṇeśvaratvam+āsādya &mayā saha nivatsyase|| 1119 ||

asmāt+yojanamātreṇa &pūrve bhāge gaṇas+mama|
tvayā sārdham+nivatsyāmi &bhūtvā bhūteśvaras+haras+|| 1120 ||

tava nandin+pratiṣṭhānam+ &vasiṣṭhas+bhagavān+ṛṣis+|
kartā deśe śubhe tasmin+ &mama ca+api+uta bhūtale|| 1121 ||

saṃnidhānam+kariṣyāmas+ &tatra nityam+vayam+dvija|
pūrvotpannas+sa jyeṣṭheśas+ &tatra liṅgas+mama dvija|| 1122 ||

tatra+api saṃnidhānam+me &nityam+vijñātum+arhasi|
ṛṣikoṭisahasrāṇi &mama bhaktyā dvijottama|| 1123 ||

tatra saṃsnāpayanti sma &jyeṣṭheśam+te sadā+eva tu|
brahman+divyena toyena &śubhena+uttaramānasāt|| 1124 ||

teṣām+tapaḥprabhāvena &bhaktyā ca mama pārṣada|
sodarasya ca nāgasya &sthānam+uttaramānasas+|| 1125 ||

svayam+prāptas+mahābhāga &tatra raṃsyasi sarvadā|
yasmāt+deśāt+tathā yāti &dakṣiṇena mahānadī|| 1126 ||

hiraṇyinī puṇyajalā &nāmnā kanakavāhinī|
jyeṣṭheśe vasate bhūtais+ &vasa prākāmyatas+dvija|| 1127 ||

matsamīpam+atha+abhyehi &dehena+anyena putraka|
evam+uktvā tu deveśas+ &nandinam+praṇatam+sthitam|| 1128 ||

mṛtyum+visarjayāmāsa &sāntvayitvā surārihā|
nandinam+ca samādāya &dṛṣṭvā ca+uttaramānasam|| 1129 ||

tasya+eva sarasas+abhyāśe &śṛṅgam+trailokyaviśrutam|
haramukuṭam+iti khyātam+ &āruroha mudā+anvitas+|| 1130 ||

tatra saṃnihitas+nityam+ &devadevas+maheśvaras+|
jyeṣṭheśvarasamīpe tu &vasiṣṭhas+api mahāyaśās+|| 1131 ||

sarvais+devagaṇais+sārdham+ &cakre bhūteśvaram+haram|
tasya+eva paścimām+mūrtim+ &sa cakāra+atha nandinam|| 1132 ||

evam+kṛte yayus+devās+ &yathāgatam+ariṃdama|
cakrus+tīrthāni ca tathā &ṛṣayas+ca tapodhanās+|| 1133 ||

evam+hi bhṛguśāpena &harasya+anugraheṇa ca|
tatra saṃnihitas+nandī &tatprītyā ca maheśvaras+|| 1134 ||

nandīśvarasya yā mūrtis+ &durācārais+na dṛśyate|
bhūteśvaram+tathā dṛṣṭvā &mucyate sarvakilbiṣais+|| 1135 ||

snātvā tu sodare puṇye &dṛṣṭvā bhūteśvaram+haram|
jyeṣṭheśvaram+nandinam+ca &gāṇapatyam+avāpnuyāt|| 1136 ||

iti nīlamate bhūteśvaramāhātmyam|

gonandas+uvāca |

kapaṭeśvaram+iti+uktam+ &devadevasya śūlinas+|
puṇyam+āyatanam+tasya &samutpattim+vadasva me|| 1137 ||

saṃśayas+me mahān+brahman+ &kapaṭeśvarakīrtanāt|
kimartham+bhagavan+śambhus+ &procyate kapaṭeśvaras+|| 1138 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

puṇye dṛṣadvatītīre &kurukṣetre narādhipa|
ṛṣikoṭyas+samuttasthus+ &tapas+paramam+āsthitās+|| 1139 ||

draṣṭum+deveśvaram+rudram+ &tadbhaktyā parameśvara|
tān+āha bhagavān+svapne &kaśmīrām+drutam+āśugās+|| 1140 ||

vrajadhvam+yatra nāgasya &bhavanam+vimalam+mahat|
kapaṭe tatra dāsyāmi &darśanam+bhavatām+aham|| 1141 ||

etat+svapne niśamya+atha &kalyam+uktvā parasparam|
kaśmīrām+sahitās+jagmus+ &śambhum+devam+didṛkṣavas+|| 1142 ||

te prāpya tasya nāgasya &bhavanam+jalam+anu+api|
na paśyanti jale kāṣṭhais+ &sarvatas+parivārite|| 1143 ||

tatra kāṣṭhāni saṃcālya &karais+te ṛṣisattamās+|
snātamātrās+yayus+sarve &svaśarīreṇa rudratām|| 1144 ||

vāsiṣṭhas+brāhmaṇas+tu+ekas+ &nāmnā gauraparāśaras+|
na sasnau na ca tat+kāṣṭham+ &spṛśati sma kutūhalāt|| 1145 ||

tatrasthas+śoṣayāmāsa &nirāhāras+kalevaram|
tam+uvāca haras+svapne &kimartham+dvija kliśyasi|| 1146 ||

snātvā saṃspṛśya kāṣṭhāni &śīghram+tvam+vraja rudratām|
iti+uktas+asau tadā svapne &śambhunā parameṣṭhinā|| 1147 ||

tam+uvāca dvijas+rudram+ &prayatas+prāñjalis+sthitas+|
satyam+rudratvam+āsādya &dṛśyase tvam+jagadguro|| 1148 ||

kim+tu+adṛṣṭe hi deveśe &na+asti me manasas+dhṛtis+|
kapaṭe bhavatām+dāsye &tvayā+uktam+darśanam+prabho|| 1149 ||

tat+aprāpya na yāsyāmi &na ca bhokṣyāmi śaṃkara|
tam+uvāca tatas+bhūyas+ &śaṃkaras+prahasan+iva|| 1150 ||

dattam+tu kāṣṭharūpeṇa &mayā teṣām+tu darśanam|
te mām+dṛṣṭvā+eva samprāptās+ &rudratvam+tat+tathā dvija|| 1151 ||

tava+adhikena tapasā &varam+dadmi tava+īpsitam|
tat+tvam+varaya bhadram+te &rudratām+ca tathā vraja|| 1152 ||

gauraparāśaras+uvāca |

varas+cet+dīyate deva &mama kāmāṅganāśana|
ṛṣibhis+tvam+yathā dṛṣṭas+ &kāṣṭharūpe maheśvara|| 1153 ||

tathā tvam+dehi sarvasya &janasya+iha nidarśanam|
sarvakālam+jagannātha &lokas+kliśyati pāpmanā|| 1154 ||

maheśvaras+uvāca |

drakṣyanti ye janās+mām+vai &kāṣṭharūpam+samāsthitam|
kadācit+dvijaśārdūla &sarvakālam+tu na+u dvija|| 1155 ||

[lacuna] &[lacuna]|
ayam+ca satatam+nandī &kāṣṭharūpe gaṇas+mama|
darśanam+dāsyate nṛṇām+ &tadanugrahakāmyayā|| 1156 ||

tam+na dṛṣṭvā ca yāsyanti &svaśarīreṇa rudratām|
kapaṭena ca dāsyāmi &narāṇām+darśanam+yadā|| 1157 ||

tadā saṃjñām+avāpsyāmi &kapaṭeśvaras+iti+uta|
toyasya bahulībhāvas+ &deśe+asmin+brāhmaṇottama|| 1158 ||

darśanasya madīyasya &pūrvarūpam+bhaviṣyati|
iti+etat+kathitam+tubhyam+ &kapaṭeśvarasambhavam|| 1159 ||

gonandas+uvāca |

bhagavan śrotum+icchāmi &viṣṇos+āyatanāni+aham|
kaśmīrāyām+phalam+teṣām+ &yeṣu saṃnihitas+haris+|| 1160 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

nityam+saṃnihitas+devas+ &rājan+cakradharas+haris+|
tam+dṛṣṭvā puṇḍarīkākṣam+ &daśadhenuphalam+labhet|| 1161 ||

nityam+saṃnihitas+devas+ &narasiṃhas+janārdanas+|
tam+dṛṣṭvā devadeveśam+ &aśvamedhaphalam+labhet|| 1162 ||

devas+saṃnihitas+rājan+ &nityam+bahusaras+tathā|
tathā saṃnihitas+rājan+ &puṇye devasare śubhe|| 1163 ||

vāsiṣṭhāyām+atha+eva+atra &kadrvarcāyām+tathā+eva ca|
vinatārcāyām+saṃnihitam+ &gautamyām+pārthivottama|
etās+dṛṣṭvā keśavārcās+ &agniṣṭomaphalam+labhet|| 1164 ||

mahāpadmasya sarasas+ &puṇye kūle tathā+uttare|
nṛsiṃham+aparam+dṛṣṭvā &vahniṣṭomaphalam+labhet|| 1165 ||

devam+śakrakṛtam+dṛṣṭvā &varuṇena tathā kṛtam|
brahmaṇā ca dhaneśena &yamena ca hareṇa ca|| 1166 ||

divākareṇa somena &vahninā pavanena ca|
kaśyapena+atha bhṛgunā &pulastyena tathā+atriṇā|| 1167 ||

bhūrjasvāmim+mahāsvāmim+ &śataśṛṅgagadādharam|
meros+bhavanapārśve ca &bhṛgusvāmim+janārdanam|| 1168 ||

taittirīyeśvaram+devam+ &daṇḍakasvāminam+tathā|
bhavasya ca tathā pārśve &rāmasvāmim+janārdanam|| 1169 ||

devam+nārāyaṇasthānam+ &paścime tu varapradam|
gajendramokṣaṇam+devam+ &varāhasya samīpagam|| 1170 ||

varāham+ca nṛsiṃham+ca &bahurūpam+varapradam|
saptarṣīṇām+tathā+eva+arcās+ &sumukhasya samīpagās+|| 1171 ||

tuṅgavāsam+ca varadam+ &varadam+ca svayambhuvam|
guhāvāsam+ca yogeśam+ &anantam+kapilam+munim|| 1172 ||

aśvaśīrṣam+tathā matsyam+ &haṃsam+kūrmam+tathā+eva ca|
utaṅkasvāminam+devam+ &vālakhilyakṛtam+tathā|| 1173 ||

garuḍam+jalavāsam+ca &devam+bhogamayam+tathā|
dṛṣṭvā+ekaikam+atha+etebhyas+ &daśadhenuphalam+labhet|| 1174 ||

vainyena pṛthunā pūrvam+ &magadheṣu pratiṣṭhitam|
dṛṣṭvā+avāpnoti hi phalam+ &puṇḍarīkasya mānavas+|| 1175 ||

gṛdhrakūṭe tathā+eva+arcām+ &tathā bhṛgukṛtām+śubhām|
āśramasvāmim+iti+uktām+ &parvatāt+avatāritām|| 1176 ||

svadeśapārśve rāmeṇa &bhārgaveṇa mahātmanā|
dṛṣṭvā+eva sarvapāpebhyas+ &mucyate na+atra saṃśayas+|| 1177 ||

gonandas+uvāca |

gṛdhrakūṭāt+giriśreṣṭhāt+ &kimartham+bhṛgunirmitā|
arcā+avatāritā brahman+ &svāśramasya samīpatas+|| 1178 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

purā pitṛvadhāt+arcām+ &rāmas+kṣatriyamardanas+|
triḥsaptakṛtvas+pṛthivīm+ &kṛtvā niḥkṣatriyām+purā|| 1179 ||

ekaviṃśatime ghāte &prāpte kecit+tu kṣatriyās+|
giridurgam+anuprāptās+ &kaśmīrāyām+nṛpottama|| 1180 ||

rāmas+anupadam+āgamya &tān+jaghāna+atiroṣitas+|
tebhyas+api kṣatriyās+kecit+ &hataśeṣās+mahīpate|| 1181 ||

tadbhayena+āgatās+tyaktvā &kaśmīrām+rājasattama|
nadī madhumatī yatra &tathā+anyā rajanirmalā|
tathā+api rāmas+tān+gatvā &ghātayāmāsa roṣatas+|| 1182 ||

niḥśeṣān+kṣatriyān+hatvā &rudhirāktakaras+tatas+|
pratiṣṭhām+akarot+rājan+ &keśavasya mahātmanas+|| 1183 ||

rājāvāsam+iti proktam+ &sarvalokeṣu viśrutam|
tam+dṛṣṭvā śīghram+āpnoti &kāryasiddhim+narottama|| 1184 ||

raudrabhāvena rāmeṇa &yadā ca+arcā vinirmitā|
raudrabhāvam+atha+āsthāya &tasyām+saṃnihitas+haris+|| 1185 ||

arcayanti ca raudreṇa &tam+ca bhāvena mānavās+|
raudrabhāvāt+mahīnātha &nityam+paśuvadhādinā|| 1186 ||

tatas+rāmas+api dharmātmā &pūrvam+kṣatriyaśoṇitais+|
kṛtān+kuṇḍān+jagāma+atha &kurukṣetre mahīpate|| 1187 ||

pitṛn+sa teṣu+atha+abhyarcya &mudam+lebhe surārihā|
tam+ūcus+pitaras+prītās+ &rāma rāma mahābhuja|| 1188 ||

karmaṇā+ugrān+nivartasva &tīrthayātrām+tathā kuru|
palāyamānān+bhītān+ca &hatavān+asi pārthivān|| 1189 ||

tena pāpena te putra &śarīram+kaluṣam+yadā|
tasmāt+vrajasva tīrthāni &pāvanārtham+iha+ātmanas+|| 1190 ||

bhaviṣyasi yathāvat+tvam+ &śuddhadehas+ca putraka|
na+apaiṣyati hi te tāvat+ &karebhyas+rudhiram+dṛḍham|| 1191 ||

yadā karau virudhirau &tava putra bhaviṣyatas+|
tadā tvam+nirmalībhūtas+ &tapas+kuru yathāsukham|| 1192 ||

evam+uktas+tadā rāmas+ &pitṛbhis+pūjitas+tatas+|
cakāra tīrthayātrām+vai &sarvatīrtheṣu pārthiva|| 1193 ||

kṛtvā jagāma kaśmīrām+ &tathā+api sa mahīpate|
āplutya tīrtheṣu tadā &gṛdhrakūṭam+upāgamat|| 1194 ||

śuddhā sarasvatī ca+eva &saṃyogam+yatra gacchatas+|
tatra snātasya rāmasya &karau śuddhim+upāgatau|| 1195 ||

tasya tīrthasya rāmas+api &varam+prādāt+mahāyaśās+|
asmin+tīrthe naras+snātvā &sarvam+mokṣyati kilbiṣam|| 1196 ||

śuddhadehas+tadā gantā &bhṛgūṇām+samalokatām|
evam+tu nirmalībhūtas+ &rāmas+parabalārdanas+|| 1197 ||

patheśvaram+atha+āsādya &tapas+tepe sudāruṇam|
nadīm+samprāpya puṇyodām+ &tadā brahmasarodbhavām|| 1198 ||

yadā tasyām+tu rāmeṇa &tapas+taptam+mahātmanā|
tadā rāmahradā+iti+evam+ &nadī sā bhuvi viśrutā|| 1199 ||

tatra saṃvatsaram+kṛtvā &rāmas+api paramam+tapas+|
taportham+gṛdhrakūṭasya &tadā mūlam+jagāma sas+|| 1200 ||

yatra+asya ca+āgatau śuddhim+ &karau pūrvam+mahīpate|
tasmāt+adūre puṇyode &anantasya mahātmanas+|| 1201 ||

bhavane nāgarājasya &tapas+tepe sudāruṇam|
pratiṣṭhānam+tathā cakre &tasya devasya śārṅgiṇas+|| 1202 ||

tatra+asatas+tatas+tasya &rāmasya+akliṣṭakarmaṇas+|
āśramasvāminam+draṣṭum+ &prayayau brāhmaṇottamas+|| 1203 ||

dātum+gām+tasya devasya &tām+ādāya tu satvaras+|
tatra+asau+apathe prāṇān+ &tasmin+tatyāja parvate|| 1204 ||

tyaktvā ca gām+mahīnātha &brāhmaṇas+api nivartitas+|
prāyaścittīyatām+prāpya &duḥkhaśokasamanvitas+|| 1205 ||

sa rāmāśramam+āgatya &vāsiṣṭhas+dharmaniścalas+|
yathāvṛttam+atha+ācakhyau &rāmāya sumahātmane|| 1206 ||

tam+uvāca tatas+rāmas+ &paśyan+divyena cakṣuṣā|
divyotpannā dvijaśreṣṭha &divyanārī manoramā|
devarṣim+vañcayāmāsa &gorūpeṇa+atha nāradam|| 1207 ||

tena vijñāya sā śaptā &tava gotvam+upāgata|
tena+eva tasya śāpāntas+ &kṛtas+brāhmaṇasattama|| 1208 ||

gosvāminā nīyamānā &gṛdhrakūṭe śiloccaye|
tanum+tyaktvā tatas+bhūyas+ &bhaviṣyasi varāpsarās+|| 1209 ||

mokṣitā sā tvayā śāpāt+ &na te+asti dvija pātakam|
godānaphalasaṃyuktas+ &matprasādāt+bhaviṣyasi|| 1210 ||

gaccha paśya svadeveśam+ &tathā+āśramanivāsinam|
tam+dṛṣṭvā sarvapāpebhyas+ &vinirmuktas+bhaviṣyasi|| 1211 ||

aham+hi devapravaram+ &ārādhya madhusūdanam|
iha+ānayiṣye tām+arcām+ &lokasya hitakāmyayā|| 1212 ||

ānītāyām+iha+arcāyām+ &dvijendra na bhaviṣyati|
tasmin+eva tadā sthāne &tapas+tepe sa bhārgavas+|| 1214 ||

tatas+saṃvatsarasya+ante &dadarśa madhusūdanam|
divyena cakṣuṣā rājan+ &prasannam+agratas+sthitam|| 1215 ||

tuṣāracayasaṃkāśam+ &śvetāmbaravibhūṣitam|
mukuṭena+arkavarṇena &kuṇḍalais+ca virājitam|| 1216 ||

caturmukham+caturbāhum+ &caturvedāśrayānvitam|
śarīradhāribhis+ca+astrais+ &udīritajayasvanam|| 1217 ||

tam+dṛṣṭvā praṇatas+rājan+ &tuṣṭāva madhusūdanam|

rāmas+uvāca |

namas+te devadeveśa &praṇatārtivināśana|| 1218 ||

caturmūrte mahāmūrte &caturveda mahābhuja|
govinda puṇḍarīkākṣa &varāha+ādya namas+astu te|| 1219 ||

daṃṣṭrāgroddhṛtabhūbhāra &saṃcūrṇitaśiloccaya|
tvam+sadā+eva varāhas+asi &yena+idam+dhāryate jagat|| 1220 ||

karajāgravinirbhinna- &hiraṇyakaśipūrase|
namas+tubhyam+nṛsiṃhāya &jvālāmālākulātmane|| 1221 ||

trivikramāya devāya &namas+te vijigīṣave|
somabhūṣitavaktrāya &namas+aśvaśirase prabho|| 1222 ||

tvam+deva sarvadevānām+ &duḥkhitānām+parā gatis+|
indriyāṇi+indriyārthās+ca &mahābhūtāni yāni ca|| 1223 ||

manas+buddhis+tathā+eva+ātmā &avyaktam+puruṣodbhavam|
sattvam+rajas+tamas+ca+eva &brahmā viṣṇus+maheśvaras+|| 1224 ||

tvayā sarvam+idam+vyāptam+ &trailokyam+sacarācaram|
tvayā vinā na paśyāmi &kiṃcit+eva jagattraye|| 1225 ||

tvattejasā mayā deva &nihatās+kṣatriyās+bhuvi|
koṭisaṃkhyās+ca nihatās+ &saiṃhikeyās+mahābalās+|| 1226 ||

sūkṣmātisūkṣma deveśa &mahadbhyas+api mahattara|
kṣīrodakanyādayita &kāmarūpa namas+astu te|| 1227 ||

kāmakāmada kāmāri- &pūjita+aghavināśana|
caturbhis+satatam+vaktrais+ &padmajanmābhisaṃstuta|| 1228 ||

kām+aham+te kariṣyāmi &jagatkāraṇakāraṇa|
stutim+trailokyanātha+īśa &sarvathā+eva namas+astu te|| 1229 ||

namas+pārśveṣu te deva &namas+te sarvatas+prabho|
parvateṣu samudreṣu &lokeṣu gagane tathā|
namas+te+astu namas+te+astu &sarvatra+eva namas+astu te|| 1230 ||

evam+stutas+tu rāmeṇa &rāmam+āha janārdanas+|
rāma rāma mahābāho &varam+varaya suvrata|| 1231 ||

vīryeṇa tapasā deva- &stotreṇa+anena suvrata|
parituṣṭas+asmi te vatsa &yathā na+anyasya kasyacit|| 1232 ||

rāmas+uvāca |

bhṛgunā nirmitām+arcām+ &gṛdhrakūṭāgratas+prabho|
iha+ānayitum+icchāmi &tat+me+anujñātum+arhasi|| 1233 ||

bhagavān+uvāca |

evam+kuru yatheṣṭam+te &janas+mucyeta kilbiṣāt|
kleśam+vinā bhṛguśreṣṭha &kṛtas+te+anugrahas+mayā|| 1234 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

evam+uktvā yayau viṣṇus+ &tadā+antardhānam+īśvaras+|
rāmas+api gṛdhrakūṭāt+tām+ &tadarcām+avatārayat|| 1235 ||

madhye cakāra tām+bhaktyā &svārcām+anantakūṭayos+|
tām+dṛṣṭvā phalam+āpnoti &puṇḍarīkasya mānavas+|| 1236 ||

rāmas+api tapasā dīptas+ &vājimedhe mahākratau|
dattvā mahīm+kaśyapāya &mahendram+parvatam+gatas+|| 1237 ||

evam+rāmena dharmajña &gṛdhrakūṭāt+nagottamāt|
svāśramasya samīpe tu &ānītā pratimā śubhā|| 1238 ||

iti nīlamate āśramasvāmimāhātmyam|

gonandas+uvāca |

deśasya+asya samīpe tu &tīrthāni vadatām+vara|
kathayasva+amitaprajña &tasmin+tīrthe phalam+ca kim|| 1239 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

āruhya gṛdhrakūṭam+tu &gosahasraphalam+labhet|
kusunārīm+nadīm+prāpya &snātas+mucyeta kilbiṣais+|| 1240 ||

kṛṣṇāvitastāsaṃyoge &gosahasraphalam+labhet|
vitastāmadhumatyos+ca &saṃgame tridivam+vrajet|| 1241 ||

indrakīlam+samāruhya &gosahasraphalam+labhet|
tathā madhumatītīre &śāṇḍilyena niveśitam|
dṛṣṭvā cakreśam+āpnoti &vahniṣṭomaphalam+naras+|| 1242 ||

tathā madhumatītīre &śāṇḍilyena niveśitām|
dṛṣṭvā durgām+avāpnoti &kāmam+eva yathepsitam|| 1243 ||

tatra+eva śāṇḍilī nāma &nadī pāpanisūdanī|
tasyām+snātas+divam+yāti &puruṣas+gatakalmaṣas+|| 1244 ||

śāṇḍilīmadhumatyos+ca &snātas+yas+saṃgame naras+|
sarvapāpavinirmuktas+ &svargalokam+sa gacchati|| 1245 ||

rājāvāsam+harim+dṛṣṭvā &kāmam+āpnoti+abhīpsitam|
rajovinirmalam+prāpya &snātvā mucyeta kilbiṣais+|| 1246 ||

tasyām+devī umā snātā &prathamam+tu rajovatī|
dṛṣṭvā tu gaurīśikharam+ &candralokam+avāpnuyāt|| 1247 ||

pūrvam+āsīt+umā rājan+ &nīlotpalasamaprabhā|
sā tatra tapasā lebhe &gauram+varṇam+manoharam|| 1248 ||

kṛṣṇapakṣe+api tam+śailam+ &sajyotsnam+iva mānada|
paśyanti mānavās+nityam+ &tatra vai mahat+adbhutam|| 1249 ||

trisaṃdhyām+rudrasaṃdhyām+ca &snānam+kṛtvā ca mānavas+|
gosahasram+avāpnoti &viṣṇuloke mahīyate|| 1250 ||

telalām+bhūrjalām+puṇyām+ &avagāhya pṛthak+pṛthak|
tulyam+phalam+avāpnoti &gośatasya sa mānavas+|
tayos+tu saṃgame snātvā &vājapeyaphalam+labhet|| 1251 ||

madhumatyām+tayos+ca+eva &snātasya nṛpa saṃgame|
kathitam+munibhis+puṇyam+ &aśvadānasya yat+phalam|| 1252 ||

tathā prabhavam+āsādya &madhumatyās+manoharam|
sarvapāpavinirmuktas+ &rudraloke mahīyate|| 1253 ||

uttare mānase snātvā &gosahasraphalam+labhet|
pitaras+tarpitās+tatra &kāmān+yacchanti+abhīpsitān|| 1254 ||

haramuṇḍe naras+snātvā &daśagodaphalam+labhet|
āruhya tat+avāpnoti &rājasūyaphalam+naras+|| 1255 ||

tatra gaṅgā sarit+śreṣṭhā &candrabhraṣṭā pratiṣṭhitā|
yasyām+snātasya pūyante &sarvapāpāni+asaṃśayam|| 1256 ||

rājasūyam+avāpnoti &gaṅgāmānasasaṃgame|
[lacuna] &[lacuna]|| 1257 ||

devatīrthe naras+snātvā &bhavaty dashdashdash|
vālakhilyakṛte+agastye &tulyatejās+maharṣibhis+|| 1258 ||

kālodakam+nandikuṇḍam+ &śaṅkhacakrau gadām+tathā|
padmam+sakapilātīrtham+ &tīrthau vāṭikaśaṇḍikau|| 1259 ||

tīrtham+apsarasām+puṇyam+ &brahmaṇas+parameṣṭhinas+|
kṛpāṇītīrtham+āsādya &pratyekam+gośatam+labhet|| 1260 ||

kālodakam+yatra yāti &nadī mānasasambhavā|
tatra snātasya pūyante &sarvapāpāni+aśeṣatas+|| 1261 ||

devavadhvas+tathā puṇyās+ &puṇyam+sūryasaras+smṛtam|
tārāsaras+candrasaras+ &puṇyam+kāluṣakam+mahat|| 1262 ||

brahmaṇas+yāgabhūmis+ca &tatra puṇyā mahīpate|
cakratīrtham+devatīrtham+ &tīrtham+brāhmaṇakuṇḍikā|| 1263 ||

dṛṣṭvā+aikaikyam+atha+etebhyas+ &gośatasya phalam+labhet|
haṃsadvāram+tu saṃgamya &svargam+āpnoti+asaṃśayam|| 1264 ||

sindhos+prabhavam+āsādya &rājasūyaphalam+labhet|
puṇḍarīkam+avāpnoti &snātvā bindusarasi+api|| 1265 ||

maḍavāyām+naras+snātvā &gosahasraphalam+labhet|
saṃdhyām+nāma nadīm+dṛṣṭvā &mucyate sarvakilbiṣais+|| 1266 ||

aśraddadhānam+na+abhyeti &sādhu+abhītya dṛḍhavratam|
tatra+agnitīrtham+dṛṣṭvā+eva &vahniloke mahīyate|| 1267 ||

nadī citrapathā puṇyā &mṛgānandā tathā mṛgā|
godāvarī vaitaraṇī &tathā mandākinī śubhā|| 1268 ||

candrabhāgā gotamī ca &sarvapāpabhayāpahā|
pṛthak+etāsu+avāpnoti &gośatasya phalam+naras+|| 1269 ||

yatra citrapathā puṇyā &maḍavā ca mahānadī|
ekībhavanti snātasya &tatra naśyati kilbiṣam|| 1270 ||

svargalokam+avāpnoti &punāti svakulam+naras+|
tathā ca+etās+mahānadyas+ &kathitās+te mahīpate|| 1271 ||

tāsām+tu saṃgamās+puṇyās+ &svargalokaphalapradās+|
citrakūṭas+giris+puṇyas+ &umā yatra vivāhitā|| 1272 ||

tatra+anulepanam+divyam+ &yadāliptatanus+naras+|
surūpabhāgī bhavati &subhagas+ca+eva jāyate|| 1273 ||

tatra gavyasaras+tatra &pañcagavyasaras+pṛthak|
tatra+anye sapta bhūpāla &puṇyam+tailasaras+tathā|| 1274 ||

udvartanasaras+puṇyam+ &puṇyam+ca atasīsaras+|
siddhārthakasaras+tatra &tathā+āmalakavāriṇā|| 1275 ||

madhuparkasaras+puṇyam+ &puṇyam+uṣṇodakam+tathā|
ekam+ekam+atha+etebhyas+ &dṛṣṭvā svarlokam+āpnuyāt|| 1276 ||

citrakūṭam+atha+āruhya &svargaloke mahīyate|
tīrtham+saptaṛṣim+nāma &sarvakāmaphalapradam|| 1277 ||

aśvamedhasahasrasya &rājasūyaśatasya ca|
gavām+śatasahasrasya &śreyān+saptaṛṣes+carus+|| 1278 ||

śrāddham+dānam+tathā japyam+ &snānam+homam+tathā+arcanam|
sarvam+akṣayatām+yāti &yat+kṛtam+tatra pārthiva|| 1279 ||

vastrāpadam+atha+āsādya &rudraloke mahīyate|
chāgaleśvaram+āsādya &kāmam+āpnoti+abhīpsitam|| 1280 ||

rudrasya+anucaras+bhūtvā &tena+eva saha modate|
paroṣṇīprabhavam+prāpya &gosahasraphalam+labhet|| 1281 ||

karkoṭake naras+snātvā &daśagodaphalam+labhet|
sahasradhāram+āsādya &viṣṇuloke mahīyate|| 1282 ||

kramatā viṣṇunā lokān+ &kṛtam+pādena tat+saras+|
kramasāram+idam+proktam+ &yathā viṣṇupadam+ca tat|| 1283 ||

iṣṭavān+kratubhis+tatra &yadā devas+pitāmahas+|
kramasāras+tadā proktas+ &sarvakalmaṣanāśanas+|| 1284 ||

vasatis+tatra nāgasya &kauṇḍinyasya yadā tadā|
kauṇḍinyasaras+iti+eva &tasya nāma prakīrtitam|| 1285 ||

tatra snātvā samabhyarcya &devatās+pitaras+tathā|
dṛṣṭvā tu śikharān+ramyān+ &brahmaviṣṇumaheśvarān|| 1286 ||

lokatrayam+avāpnoti &teṣām+eva na saṃśayas+|
brahmaṇas+yāgabhūmim+tu &dṛṣṭvā tatra mahīpate|| 1287 ||

svargalokam+avāpnoti &kulam+uddharate svakam|
tatra kṣīrasaras+ramyam+ &dṛṣṭvā mucyeta kilbiṣais+|| 1288 ||

samārāprabhavam+prāpya &snātvā kṛṣṇacaturdaśīm|
sarvapāpavinirmuktas+ &rudraloke mahīyate|| 1289 ||

saṃnikṛṣṭāni tīrthāni &kathitāni mayā tava|
sarveṣām+pāpahartṛni &kim+bhūyas+kathayāmi te|| 1290 ||

gonandas+uvāca |

tīrthāni dvija mukhyāni &kaśmīrāyām+vadasva me|
teṣām+snāne ca yat+puṇyam+ &tapasā dagdhakilbiṣa|| 1291 ||

bṛhadaśvas+uvāca |

niḥsṛtā sarasas+puṇyā &kramasārāt+mahānadī|
kauṇḍinyā nāma yā snāne &puṇḍarīkaphalapradā|| 1292 ||

tathā kṣīranadī puṇyā &gośatasya phalapradā|
tayos+samāgame snātvā &gosahasraphalam+labhet|| 1293 ||

viśokāyām+naras+snātvā &viśokas+śrīsamanvitas+|
phalam+puṇyam+avāpnoti &devasattrasya mānavas+|| 1294 ||

kauṇḍinī saha saṃyogam+ &yatra yāti viśokayā|
tatra snātasya rājendra &vājapeyaphalam+bhavet|| 1295 ||

vṛddhatīrthe naras+snātvā &yajñam+āpnoti gosavam|
tatra saṃnihitas+nityam+ &vāsukis+bhujagādhipas+|| 1296 ||

devalokam+avāpnoti &snātvā devasarasi+api|
agnitīrthe naras+snātvā &vahnilokam+prapadyate|| 1297 ||

nadī sarasvatī nāma &yasyām+snātas+divam+vrajet|
pūrvadakṣiṇabhāge tu &sthitā devasarasi+api|| 1298 ||

vinatāsvāmipuratas+ &kadrūsvāmisamīpatas+|
tīrthayos+tu naras+snātvā &gośatasya phalam+labhet|| 1299 ||

saṃdhyā devī nadī puṇyā &yasyām+snātasya mānada|
vyapaiti kalmaṣam+dehāt+ &svargalokam+ca gacchati|| 1300 ||

saṃdhyā puṣkariṇī tu+anyā &pūrvatulyaphalapradā|
avagāhya naras+bhaktyā &puṇyām+brāhmaṇakuṇḍikām|| 1301 ||

nīlakuṇḍam+vitastākhyam+ &śūlaghātam+tathā+eva ca|
tīrtham+trināmakam+dṛṣṭvā &svargaloke mahīyate|| 1302 ||

tathā vinaśanam+prāpya &vājapeyaphalam+labhet|
brāhmaṇakuṇḍikāyām+ca &nīlakuṇḍe ca pārthiva|| 1303 ||

akṣayam+sarvam+uddiṣṭam+ &dānam+śrāddham+tathā tapas+|
vitastonmajjane snātvā &gosahasraphalam+labhet|| 1304 ||

pañcayajñān+avāpnoti &snātvā vai pañcahastake|
pratyaham+ye vinirdiṣṭās+ &gṛhasthasya mahīpate|| 1305 ||

lokapuṇyam+hi tannāma &sarvapāpaharam+param|
kāpoṭake naras+snātvā &gopradānaphalam+labhet|| 1306 ||

viṣṇvāśrame nṛsiṃhasya &puratas+pārthivottama|
vitastonmajjanam+puṇyam+ &[lacuna]|| 1307 ||

