dhaumyāśrame tayos+yoge &rājasūyaphalam+smṛtam|
caturvedīm+naras+dṛṣṭvā &kanyādānaphalam+labhet|| 1311 ||

prāpya harṣapathām+jantus+ &labhet+bahu suvarṇakam|
trikoṭiprabhavam+prāpya &mucyate sarvakilbiṣais+|| 1312 ||

prāpya candravatījanma &candraloke mahīyate|
devatīrthe naras+snātvā &divyas+putras+api jāyate|| 1313 ||

trikoṭyām+tu naras+snātvā &devaloke mahīyate|
snātvā harṣapathāyām+ca &śakraloke mahīyate|| 1314 ||

candravatyām+naras+snātvā &daśagodaphalam+labhet|
nadī harṣapathā puṇyā &tathā candravatī ca yā|| 1315 ||

saṃgamam+yatra gacchatas+ &[lacuna]|
